OL,5, Teachers are to debate a call for      
OL,6, suicide prevention training amid       
OL,7, warnings the pressures of the job are  
OL,8, leading to a "mental health emergency".
OL,10,FThe issue will be subject to a vote on 
OL,11,FSunday at the conference for teachers' 
OL,12,Funion NASUWT.                          
OL,14,FThe motion warns of a "rise in suicide,
OL,15,Fsuicide attempts and suicidal thoughts 
OL,16,Fwithin the teaching profession".       
OL,18,FIt comes as education watchdog Ofsted  
OL,19,Ffaces greater scrutiny after the       
OL,20,Fsuicide of headteacher Ruth Perry.     
